sentence: what is the highest point in the state with the capital des moines ?
sentence-with-vars: what is the highest point in the state with the capital city0 ?
sql: select highlow.highest_point from highlow where highlow.state_name in ( select state.state_name from state where state.capital = ' des moines ' ) ;
sql-with-vars: select highlow.highest_point from highlow where highlow.state_name in ( select state.state_name from state where state.capital = ' city0 ' ) ;
